wikipedia_page.main: Naomi Ogbeta (born 18 April 1998) is a British track and field athlete who competes in the triple jump. She holds a personal best of 14.15 m (set in 2018) and is a five-time British champion. She represented her country at the 2018 European Athletics Championships and the 2019 European Athletics Indoor Championships.
